STEP 2 ‚Äî every bucket will get its own teaching system

I‚Äôll show you the first.
take BUCKET A ‚Äî single symbols.

these get taught like this:

1. show the actual symbol (glyph)

‚ô≠ ‚ôØ ‚ôÆ ùÑê ùÑû ùÑ¢ ùÑ∂ etc.

2. show the ‚Äústructural rule‚Äù

like:
‚ô≠ lowers a note by one half-step.
ùÑê holds a note beyond its written duration.

3. show the ‚Äúvisual behavior‚Äù

